00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:11.180
Thomas Jefferson, who I think we can all agree,
is one of the more foundry of the Founding

00:05:11.180 --> 00:05:15.889
Fathers and therefore someone we should probably
listen to, said to the world back then that

00:05:15.889 --> 00:05:22.610
