00:12:35.470 --> 00:12:38.949
time had marched on and all was well.

00:12:38.949 --> 00:12:41.329
But these were no longer peaceful times.

00:12:41.329 --> 00:12:46.610
It was 1777, a year after America had declared
her independence from the British crown and

00:12:46.610 --> 00:12:50.920
only days after her lion-hearted general,
George Washington, had suffered a withering

00:12:50.920 --> 00:12:53.910
defeat at the Battle of Brandywine.

00:12:53.910 --> 00:13:00.650
