metal they found into British cannons, a few

00:13:04.690 --> 00:13:12.199
American patriots confiscated their own bell,
soon to be known appropriately as the 'Liberty

00:13:12.199 --> 00:13:19.730
Bell,' and hid it in the safest place they
could find--under a pile of horse manure.

00:13:19.730 --> 00:13:21.079
The gambit worked.

00:13:21.079 --> 00:13:25.949
The marauding redcoats never got their British
hands on our American Liberty.

00:13:25.949 --> 00:13:30.180
